<header class="article-header">
	<p class="article-date"><time datetime="2018-01-18T21:00:54+09:00" itemprop="datePublished">2018年01月18日</time></p>
	<h1 class="article-title" itemprop="name"><a href="http://doonroom.blog.jp/archives/74452785.html" itemprop="url">Reposer ～優子・瞳・香乃～</a></h1>
	
</header>
